reviewText: Great book, lots of good info. Get the DVD too.

Briefly, this is one of the best videos made on horse therapy. I am very glad I have it and to learn from Jack Meagher even if it is on video. Great instructional video and it has been very useful in my therapy practice.
Received on time. DVD in good shape, plays well.  Good companion piece for book of same title.  Will view several times.
